Package codeanticode.gsvideo

Interface Summary
CLibrary This JNA interface provides access to the environment variable-related functions in the C library.
GSLibraryLoader.DummyLibrary  
 

Class Summary
GSCapture Class for storing and manipulating video frames from an attached capture device such as a camera.
GSLibraryLoader  
GSMovie This class makes it possible to load movies and to play them back in many ways including looping, pausing, and changing speed.
GSMovieMaker This class makes movies from a running program.
GSPipeline This class allows to create a custom GStreamer pipeline.
GSPlayer This class makes it possible to load and play generic media content through playbin (not only movies, but also audio files, etc).
GSVideo This class contains some basic functions used by the rest of the classes in this library.
